1
00:01:32,270 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:38,000
[Episode 8]

3
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:39,280
When that day comes,

4
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:43,120
I hope you all remember
what was said on this boat today—

5
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,320
your heartfelt words

6
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,400
and lofty ambitions.

7
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,350
Stand tall

8
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,390
and be the backbone of Great Xia.

9
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,509
It was clearly just rhetoric

10
00:01:55,509 --> 00:01:56,840
to recruit scholars.

11
00:01:57,509 --> 00:01:59,039
But why, after hearing it,

12
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,230
do I feel like crying?

13
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,210
Your Majesty...

14
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,040
places such high hopes on us.

15
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:07,330
I...

16
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,090
I really...

17
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,590
How inappropriate!

18
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,590
How can an emperor

19
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,020
speak so casually?

20
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,960
Just because of the hardships,

21
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,430
you want to turn poor scholars' bodies

22
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,490
into pawns

23
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:22,430
and sacrifice their lives for you,

24
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:24,150
depose the Empress Dowager,
and get rid of Prince Duan.

25
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,560
Because you are surviving precariously,

26
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,420
you cannot express your own will.

27
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,800
You have obstacles everywhere you head,

28
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,840
so you cannot rectify court discipline.

29
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,100
As the mighty Emperor,

30
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,150
if you don't even have such courage,

31
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:36,240
how can you talk about
paying fortunes for talent,

32
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,170
pushing others to be the backbone?

33
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,079
The common people in my village—

34
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:42,120
every household—

35
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,590
all toil in the fields all day,

36
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,360
saving every grain they can,

37
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,020
yet have barely enough to eat.

38
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,090
My younger brother and sister,

39
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:53,810
starved to death during a year

40
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:57,280
of poor harvest
shortly after they were born.

41
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,030
Such heavy taxes—

42
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,960
did they truly go where they should?

43
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:09,680
The Central Army has been fighting
against Yan State for years.

44
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,240
Yet the soldier provisions

45
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,170
are mixed with 30% sand and stones.

46
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,280
As soon as I arrived in the capital,

47
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:19,010
I saw the Court of Revision beat to death
a woman crying for justice.

48
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:20,240
Your Majesty...

49
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,480
Your Majesty!

50
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,360
Have you truly opened your eyes

51
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,420
to see what I've described?

52
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,710
Li,

53
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,150
no need to say all this.

54
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:39,480
Who was it that just said

55
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,400
if they could meet the Emperor,

56
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,310
they would kowtow and offer advice
even at the cost of their lives?

57
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:44,310
Now the Emperor is right before you.

58
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,290
What's happened to all of you?

59
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,079
Gone mute?

60
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,750
His Majesty
did punish the Minister of Revenue.

61
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,010
It caused quite a stir.

62
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,490
I believe everyone has heard about it.

63
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:57,190
As for the case of the runaway horse,

64
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,190
His Majesty also found a way

65
00:03:58,190 --> 00:04:00,190
to bring
Grand Tutor Wei's family to justice.

66
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:00,590
But

67
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,680
rumors among the people say

68
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,080
it was Prince Duan's doing.

69
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,810
Every household in my hometown

70
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,590
were burning incense
praying for his blessing.

71
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,810
No matter who did it,

72
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,690
have the people's lives

73
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:14,560
improved?

74
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,490
The incense from every household

75
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:26,430
was burned in vain at the end of the day.

76
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:26,800
Li.

77
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,270
Li.

78
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,050
Defying the Emperor

79
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,120
is a capital offense.

80
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,980
I don't mind
spilling my blood on this pleasure boat

81
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,120
to prove my determination with death.

82
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:37,070
This perfectly fulfills my wish.

83
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,170
-Mr. Li.
-Wait!

84
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,330
Mr...

85
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,360
Mr. Li.

86
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,720
His Majesty came here today

87
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:47,080
not to drag everyone into court factions.

88
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:48,400
Besides,

89
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:51,070
those who hold positions without merit,

90
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:52,800
also those of the royal family,

91
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,380
their deaths mean little.

92
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:57,159
But what crime
have the common people committed?

93
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,890
The situation has become dire.

94
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,360
Unfair taxation,

95
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,850
corrupt officials,

96
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,730
rampant corruption, and empty treasury...

97
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,600
Our abilities are limited.

98
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,510
Though we have solutions,

99
00:05:09,170 --> 00:05:10,390
one hand can't clap.

100
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:12,950
That's why we need your help.

101
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,250
I'm not eloquent

102
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:18,000
and cannot speak of grand principles.

103
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,070
But besides being a consort,

104
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,560
I am also a citizen of Great Xia.

105
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,430
I love this land.

106
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:29,070
I also want to do something

107
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,600
for the people living here.

108
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,200
But I am stupid.

109
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,060
I can only implore you all.

110
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,530
This is not for any tyrant
or demonic consort,

111
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:39,990
but for...

112
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,890
our elders of our homeland,

113
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:50,470
and for our deceased brothers and sisters.

114
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:54,360
Please consider it carefully.

115
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,400
If you wish to leave,

116
00:06:19,540 --> 00:06:20,600
I will not stop you.

117
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,540
If you wish to serve as officials,

118
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:25,030
I will fully support you,

119
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,430
even if not under my command.

120
00:06:31,630 --> 00:06:32,760
I don't understand.

121
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:35,090
Why are you doing this?

122
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,330
There is no particular reason.

123
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:39,920
It's only because I believe

124
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,230
that wherever you are,

125
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,440
whatever you do,

126
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,440
you surely act for the good of Great Xia.

127
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:48,990
Even if...

128
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,760
it means opposing me.

129
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,920
I...

130
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:57,870
I...

131
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,070
I never understood before why,

132
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:03,130
when speaking to the royals,
we condescend ourselves.

133
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:06,560
Are we born to be trampled upon?

134
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:10,430
Now I understand.

135
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,750
We are just

136
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,990
ever-growing and resilient—
the foundation.

137
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:22,270
I was born with a terrible illness

138
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,890
and have only
two or three years left to live.

139
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:28,890
May I ask Your Majesty,

140
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:32,870
will I live to see peace and prosperity,

141
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,040
harmony and abundance?

142
00:07:39,850 --> 00:07:41,710
This is my promise as the Emperor.

143
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,450
I, Cen Jintian,

144
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:59,680
am willing to serve Your Majesty

145
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,810
with all my loyalty.

146
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,800
Even if they are just 2D characters,

147
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,360
the suffering they endure

148
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,920
is real pain to them.

149
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,530
I've always overlooked this fact,

150
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:30,000
thinking I was different from them.

151
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,270
But how can I be certain

152
00:08:31,290 --> 00:08:33,220
that I'm not a 2D character myself?

153
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,320
Since we're here,

154
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,700
we might as well accept it.

155
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:52,960
Hey, quick!

156
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,720
There's a leak!

157
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,250
Boatman!

158
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,560
Your boat is leaking!

159
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:00,280
Plug it!

160
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:11,480
-Mr. Yang, our boat is leaking!
-Help!

161
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,500
S-Same here!

162
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:23,960
Save them quickly!

163
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,120
Make sure to rescue all the scholars!

164
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,780
-Yes!
-Yes!

165
00:09:59,240 --> 00:09:59,660
Quick!

166
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,590
Grab it!

167
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:43,670
Xu Yao!

168
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,240
Get up!

169
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:50,000
This isn't how your story ends
in the book.

170
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:52,240
You still have a vendetta to settle.

171
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,500
You're still so young.

172
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:55,870
You must have many things you want to do.

173
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,440
In your story, your ending

174
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,670
is to be second only to one,
above thousands,

175
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,960
wealthy and healthy.

176
00:11:00,170 --> 00:11:03,160
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

177
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:03,720
I give my life to the wise master,

178
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:06,180
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

179
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:07,030
and I die for the country.

180
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:07,400
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

181
00:11:07,430 --> 00:11:10,970
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

182
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,670
I love this land.

183
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,390
I also want to do something

184
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:13,710
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

185
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,730
for the people living here.

186
00:11:13,730 --> 00:11:15,210
♪ I am the moral order ♪

187
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,320
If that's truly the case,

188
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,320
then it would fulfill

189
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:18,340
♪ The gleam of the blade
tempers feathers into a phantom Phoenix  ♪

190
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,470
my childhood aspirations.

191
00:11:18,470 --> 00:11:19,390
♪ And these Phoenix bones of mine ♪

192
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:24,350
♪ Empower me
to pierce through the wind and waves ♪

193
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:20,810
May I ask Your Majesty,

194
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:24,910
will I live to see peace and prosperity,

195
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:27,600
harmony and abundance?

196
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,600
♪ Allow me ♪

197
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:30,180
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

198
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:32,960
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

199
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:36,360
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

200
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,460
These people

201
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:38,950
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

202
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,530
must all be Prince Duan's men!

203
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:40,420
♪ Allow me ♪

204
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:41,750
And they call me the demonic consort?

205
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,130
♪ To never pause ♪

206
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:43,550
♪ Allow me ♪

207
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,730
I am nothing compared to him

208
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:45,100
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

209
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,370
when it comes to being evil.

210
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:51,180
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

211
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:46,910
But,

212
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:48,980
even if he were truly a god,

213
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,840
I would never surrender!

214
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,000
Let's get him!

215
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,380
♪ Allow me ♪

216
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:17,850
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

217
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,920
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

218
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:20,700
Come on.

219
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,720
Give me your hand

220
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:24,330
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

221
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,940
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

222
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,030
What are you hesitating for?

223
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:26,630
Hurry up!

224
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:28,510
♪ Allow me ♪

225
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,180
♪ To never pause ♪

226
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,470
♪ Allow me ♪

227
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,190
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

228
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:41,280
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

229
00:12:34,770 --> 00:12:35,250
Cen.

230
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,260
It's all right now.

231
00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:51,930
Don't leave any of them alive.

232
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:54,150
Wanyin.

233
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:57,000
Interesting.

234
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,580
Your Highness!

235
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,930
There's a skilled fighter.

236
00:13:10,930 --> 00:13:13,060
Their martial skills far exceed ours.

237
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,550
The guards will hold them back.

238
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:16,080
Please leave immediately.

239
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,360
Du...

240
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,400
It's okay now.

241
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:00,750
Cover yourself.

242
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,080
Thank you.

243
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:42,790
Compared to them,

244
00:15:44,350 --> 00:15:45,410
my pain is nothing.

245
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:51,200
Do you remember?

246
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,670
That day at Banyue House,

247
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:55,870
Du Shan said

248
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:01,890
it was his final attempt
at the imperial exam.

249
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,720
His poem

250
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,440
had just begun
to spread throughout the capital.

251
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,040
It had just given him hope...

252
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:14,240
only for him to end up like this.

253
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:24,610
Try to see it differently.

254
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,650
Sacrificing one person

255
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,800
to ensure others' survival

256
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,280
is sometimes unavoidable.

257
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:37,750
Xiahou Po...

258
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,370
No matter if he foresaw this

259
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:41,960
or tracked us here,

260
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,060
how dare he kill as soon as he got here—

261
00:16:46,270 --> 00:16:47,970
right in front of me too.

262
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,600
He simply wants to intimidate

263
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:54,060
me, an emperor
who suddenly wants to resist.

264
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:55,610
I was wondering

265
00:16:57,720 --> 00:17:00,240
what tragic past he had in his backstory

266
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,440
that made him feel compelled
by government corruption

267
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,720
to seize the throne.

268
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:07,640
But the people he just tried to kill...

269
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:11,250
are the future officials,

270
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,490
the backbone of our nation,

271
00:17:14,349 --> 00:17:16,680
and the final hope
to stabilize Great Xia.

272
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:18,089
If he is a 2D character,

273
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:21,349
then he's killing innocent people.

274
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,450
If he comes from a higher level,

275
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,060
knowing exactly who they are,

276
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:27,910
yet still choosing to kill them,

277
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,980
then it's for his own future as a warlord,

278
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:32,920
condemning countless people to death

279
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,350
during this drought.

280
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:38,750
I,

281
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,070
Yu Wanyin,

282
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:44,140
will never allow that.

283
00:17:45,050 --> 00:17:47,110
Since they call me a demonic consort,

284
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:51,950
I'll show them
what being demonic truly means.

285
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:58,210
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

286
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:03,100
Get out.

287
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,130
Your Highness.

288
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:20,030
What?

289
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:29,310
That was more than 20 men.

290
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,550
All killed by one person?

291
00:18:35,230 --> 00:18:36,760
If I hadn't left first,

292
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:40,360
would I have died there too?

293
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:43,510
It is my incompetency.

294
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:46,160
I've failed Your Highness's trust.

295
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,070
Did you see the faces

296
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,440
of those on the boat?

297
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,760
Everyone who saw their faces...

298
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,280
But please rest assured, Your Highness.

299
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,810
I will make up for my failure

300
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:05,090
and identify them as soon as possible.

301
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:10,470
Lord Fan.

302
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:13,030
What did you discover

303
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,310
at West Mountain?

304
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:19,350
I...

305
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,570
I led our men

306
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:24,290
and stopped the carriage,

307
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,790
only to discover that His Majesty

308
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:27,350
had already moved the imperial guards

309
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,830
and set up an ambush there.

310
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:35,510
Well...

311
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,110
Very well.

312
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,270
Who was

313
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:45,680
in the carriage?

314
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:47,880
It was...

315
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:48,970
It was...

316
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:50,350
It...

317
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:51,920
Who was it?

318
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,510
I-I-It was

319
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:54,770
Eunuch An!

320
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:58,320
Useless!

321
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,680
Who told me

322
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:19,320
this was a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity,

323
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:23,280
that we could act
without anyone else knowing?

324
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,400
Who told me

325
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:32,270
that we were well-prepared?

326
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:37,790
And that while it may not be foolproof,

327
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:42,510
we have a high chance of succeeding?

328
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:48,200
Was it you?

329
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,280
No, Your Highness!

330
00:20:57,790 --> 00:20:58,250
Your...

331
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:01,830
Your Highness...

332
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:02,860
Your...

333
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:07,350
You are truly my excellent strategist.

334
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:11,200
You, one person alone,
killed over a hundred of my men.

335
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:15,640
Go join them now.

336
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,180
Xiahou Dan.

337
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:45,070
I underestimated you.

338
00:21:50,170 --> 00:21:53,030
[Yongyan Hall]

339
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:57,430
Still thinking about what happened today?

340
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:01,030
After calming down,

341
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:03,570
I'm even more certain now.

342
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:04,520
Certain of what?

343
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,610
Prince Duan must be a 2D character.

344
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,300
Why do you say that?

345
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:12,440
West Mountain and East Lake are far apart.

346
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,440
Prince Duan has limited forces.

347
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:16,100
If he had a god's perspective,

348
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:18,000
knowing we were at East Lake,

349
00:22:18,310 --> 00:22:20,960
why did they send
most of their forces to West Mountain

350
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,290
to surround our decoys?

351
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,940
He wasn't completely confident either.

352
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:28,150
That's right.

353
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:32,680
And the people
who ambushed us at East Lake

354
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,300
were few in number.

355
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:37,650
They were clearly unprepared.

356
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:38,410
Otherwise,

357
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:41,880
it wouldn't have ended with
just one scholar's death.

358
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:43,880
Exactly.

359
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,640
And at East Lake,

360
00:22:47,350 --> 00:22:49,030
they clearly didn't anticipate

361
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,630
Mr. Bei's fighting ability.

362
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:53,000
Just as you said,

363
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:56,650
they killed someone in front of us

364
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,790
to intimidate us.

365
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:01,440
There's no reason they could have lost.

366
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,960
I don't believe it if their loss

367
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,700
was a calculated move too.

368
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:08,750
So

369
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:11,070
Prince Duan definitely isn't

370
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,600
someone at a level above us.

371
00:23:14,310 --> 00:23:15,110
He's exposed.

372
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:17,550
Oh no.

373
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:19,520
What's wrong?

374
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,830
He might not be
the only one who's been exposed.

375
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:22,830
Who else is there?

376
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,160
That shout of yours was impressive,

377
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:27,160
but it might have exposed you to him.

378
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,240
That's it?

379
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,400
"That's it?"

380
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:36,590
Your personal safety

381
00:23:37,590 --> 00:23:38,990
is of utmost importance.

382
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:47,130
Actually, even without my shout,

383
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:50,610
Prince Duan would have suspected me
sooner or later.

384
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,280
But I still don't understand

385
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:54,720
how our plan

386
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,540
was leaked in the first place.

387
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:01,780
Only Bei Zhou and the secret guards
knew our itinerary.

388
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:02,790
But...

389
00:24:03,110 --> 00:24:06,440
in the original story,
they protected me until the very end.

390
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,940
So it can't be them.

391
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:10,970
The scholars, before meeting us,

392
00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:12,310
had no idea who we were.

393
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:14,570
So it can't be them either.

394
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,030
Then who can it be?

395
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:21,950
Actually,
besides those people we mentioned,

396
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,880
there's one more person
who might have leaked information.

397
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,410
That's Xiahou Dan himself.

398
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:26,960
Just as he said...

399
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,600
Sacrificing one person

400
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,730
to ensure others' survival

401
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,690
is sometimes unavoidable.

402
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,820
Sacrificing one 2D character

403
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:39,010
-for greater benefits.
-Drag him out!

404
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,000
After all,

405
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,240
-he doesn't think their lives...
-Drag him out!

406
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,070
-I'm telling the truth.
-Are that important.

407
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:43,870
Your Majesty!

408
00:24:49,110 --> 00:24:50,640
They're all 2D characters—

409
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,770
all promising talents in their prime.

410
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,330
In the blink of an eye...

411
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,050
Am I overthinking this?

412
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,620
If he can't be trusted either,

413
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:11,160
then in this palace,

414
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,960
who can I trust?

415
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:13,750
What are you thinking about?

416
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:14,280
Nothing.

417
00:25:16,030 --> 00:25:17,030
I'll investigate

418
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:18,080
this slowly.

419
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:20,370
You're injured.

420
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:22,700
You need to rest properly.

421
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,550
You may leave now.

422
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:30,080
You forgot? You've fallen out of favor.

423
00:25:31,070 --> 00:25:32,150
Xie Yong'er is coming soon.

424
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:32,680
Go ahead.

425
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,360
Yes, yes.

426
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,250
Then I'll take my leave.

427
00:25:39,910 --> 00:25:40,240
Wait.

428
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,410
How are you going to explain

429
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,010
the wound on your hand?

430
00:25:51,830 --> 00:25:52,290
Get out!

431
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,610
Your Majesty, please spare me!

432
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:01,720
Which cross-eyed imperial physician

433
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,750
bandaged this

434
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,680
in such a ghastly manner?

435
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,240
It's not that bad.

436
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,320
How can His Majesty do this?

437
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:15,830
He only cares for the newcomers
and ignores those that have been around.

438
00:26:15,830 --> 00:26:17,270
Even if Master made a mistake,

439
00:26:17,270 --> 00:26:19,600
he shouldn't take it out on Your Highness.

440
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,400
I just got a small cut

441
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,400
from a broken cup.

442
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,780
How can this be blamed on His Majesty?

443
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,550
But I clearly saw it.

444
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:28,440
Madam,

445
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:31,310
I suddenly want some sweet porridge.

446
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:32,640
Could you make me a bowl?

447
00:26:39,440 --> 00:26:41,240
Madam Bei is His Majesty's person.

448
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,240
Watch what you say

449
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,720
and don't upset her.

450
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,790
I'm not afraid.

451
00:26:46,350 --> 00:26:48,080
I'm just worried about My Lady.

452
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,110
You could have been with your beloved,

453
00:26:50,110 --> 00:26:51,680
living a happy life.

454
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:55,240
But now you're trapped in this palace,

455
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:58,720
dealing with that tyrant every day.

456
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:02,140
He even has people
watching you constantly.

457
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,590
Serving the emperor is like
being with a tiger.

458
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:05,520
Watch your head.

459
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,160
How does Mei still remember

460
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:10,550
my original character
of secretly loving Prince Duan?

461
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:12,240
After being with me for so long,

462
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:13,840
why hasn't she caught on yet?

463
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:22,790
Du,

464
00:27:24,830 --> 00:27:25,440
you always

465
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,030
found me

466
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,550
stingy.

467
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:33,500
Today I bought the finest
and most expensive Huadiao wine.

468
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,920
Wherever you are,

469
00:27:36,590 --> 00:27:37,250
drink more.

470
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:46,310
In Du's lifetime,

471
00:27:47,030 --> 00:27:48,620
his ambitions were unfulfilled,

472
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:50,480
he had no way to serve his country,

473
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:52,950
and poured all his passion into poetry.

474
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:53,790
Now,

475
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:55,880
having met a wise ruler,

476
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:59,070
-we will take on Du's sincerity...
-What's wrong?

477
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:01,130
and spare no effort to help Great Xia.

478
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:02,830
Du,

479
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:05,310
just watch us.

480
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,550
After what happened,

481
00:28:10,270 --> 00:28:11,600
you must all understand

482
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:14,960
that to work with me, a puppet emperor,

483
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,540
to do something real for Great Xia

484
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:20,210
requires taking great risks.

485
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:22,080
If you wish to withdraw,

486
00:28:22,550 --> 00:28:23,810
it's understandable.

487
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,510
However,

488
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,680
you have already been involved
in confidential matters.

489
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:29,340
Forgive me,

490
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:31,020
but I cannot let you

491
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,570
return home on your own.

492
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:34,530
I hope you understand.

493
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,890
What do you mean, Your Majesty?

494
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,440
Do you want to kill us?

495
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:47,000
No.

496
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:49,440
I will find you a place

497
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,750
far from this quagmire.

498
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,110
I won't force you

499
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,110
to offer counsel

500
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,000
or act as advisors.

501
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,620
You just need to study in peace

502
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:03,970
until the situation
in the capital stabilizes.

503
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,250
No matter

504
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:06,810
who sits on the throne,

505
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:07,830
you

506
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:10,770
will still be yourselves—

507
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:13,070
honest and capable talents.

508
00:29:13,590 --> 00:29:14,590
When that time comes,

509
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:16,250
use your knowledge and skills

510
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:18,170
to become virtuous ministers

511
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:21,250
remembered for generations.

512
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:37,350
I,

513
00:29:37,810 --> 00:29:38,860
Yang Duojie...

514
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:39,640
I,

515
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:40,720
Wang Zhao...

516
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,070
I,

517
00:29:41,590 --> 00:29:42,250
Li Yunxi...

518
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:43,070
I,

519
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:43,960
Er Lan,

520
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:47,030
am willing to serve
Your Majesty with utmost loyalty

521
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:48,160
only for Great Xia's

522
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:49,270
peace.

523
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:52,160
I don't have much time left

524
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,490
and cannot wait any longer.

525
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,480
I only wish to witness Great Xia

526
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:59,840
return from darkness to light.

527
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:03,880
We pledge to serve
with all our might until our last breath.

528
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:10,640
Du.

529
00:30:11,770 --> 00:30:13,230
The six of us once promised

530
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:14,910
to be loyal to our country

531
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,760
and serve in the court together.

532
00:30:16,790 --> 00:30:17,310
Now,

533
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:19,790
you have departed

534
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:21,720
while we stayed.

535
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,000
We will do our utmost

536
00:30:24,590 --> 00:30:25,990
to support our wise ruler

537
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:28,170
in hopes of bringing peace to the land

538
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:30,480
and comfort your spirit in heaven.

539
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:31,630
Rest assured,

540
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,490
this day will come soon.

541
00:30:34,650 --> 00:30:36,980
The corrupt officials will pay the price.

542
00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:38,010
We will soon

543
00:30:39,290 --> 00:30:40,750
restore your reputation.

544
00:30:49,050 --> 00:30:59,230
[Tomb of Nameless]

545
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,720
The weather is lovely today.

546
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,070
Having you accompany me

547
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:07,680
brings me great joy.

548
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,720
Your Majesty, look.

549
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:12,920
I designed these flower arrangements
for the Flower Festival Banquet.

550
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,830
They're all the most precious varieties

551
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:16,890
symbolizing prosperity and wealth.

552
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:20,440
These flowers are indeed precious.

553
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:23,870
But when arranged together,

554
00:31:24,310 --> 00:31:26,510
they look somewhat disorganized.

555
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:29,350
Then Your Highness, please look at mine.

556
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:30,960
These are all jasmine flowers

557
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,680
with an enchanting fragrance.

558
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,740
Please smell them.

559
00:31:36,510 --> 00:31:38,570
Jasmine indeed has a pure fragrance.

560
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:42,790
But they look somewhat plain

561
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,640
and rather shabby.

562
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,160
Then, Your Highness,

563
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,750
please look at these.

564
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:50,110
Do you like orchids?

565
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:54,010
Orchids from secluded valleys
have extraordinary elegance.

566
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:57,240
Orchids are indeed refined.

567
00:31:58,200 --> 00:32:00,750
But we must consider the symbolism.

568
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:03,400
After all,
they will be displayed in the palace.

569
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:06,060
They should convey
grandeur and magnificence.

570
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,440
Yes.

571
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,240
A talented scholar's life

572
00:32:10,510 --> 00:32:12,510
is worth no more
than a handful of wildflowers.

573
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:14,040
Yet to please the powerful,

574
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:16,110
we exhaust ourselves thinking,

575
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:17,270
wasting resources
and burdening the people.

576
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,000
Consort Xie,

577
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:19,880
what have you prepared?

578
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:23,400
Your Majesty,

579
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,290
I prepared peonies.

580
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:31,030
Peonies?

581
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:34,310
Isn't that too common?

582
00:32:35,030 --> 00:32:35,510
Right?

583
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:37,000
You are right.

584
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,490
Though this flower is common,

585
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:41,390
the Flower Festival Banquet

586
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:43,190
happens only once a year.

587
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:46,570
This is about
Her Majesty's reputation.

588
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,640
Her Majesty said

589
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:52,110
we must not only consider
whether it is precious or not,

590
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,970
but also their symbolic meaning.

591
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:56,480
They cannot appear too shabby either.

592
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,000
Beautiful peony,

593
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:05,790
amidst a cluster of a hundred flowers

594
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:07,920
your stunning radiance blooms alone.

595
00:33:12,070 --> 00:33:12,750
Peony,

596
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,550
with the essence of all fragrances combined,

597
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:18,110
fully displaying the grandeur of a prosperous age.

598
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:20,440
Though they speak of your delicacy, laden with dew,

599
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,400
your gentleness

600
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:25,040
is like the spring breeze bringing warmth.

601
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:28,110
Though they praise your nobility and overflowing scent—

602
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:29,030
do they know?

603
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:32,930
You have also endured the deepest cold and hardship.

604
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:35,110
When the freezing snow sealed the earth,

605
00:33:35,110 --> 00:33:37,640
you were quietly nurturing a thousand hopes.

606
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:40,550
And when the East Wind brushes the face,

607
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,320
you take your prosperity

608
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:47,550
and scatter it across the world.

609
00:33:51,750 --> 00:33:54,410
She recited
that long paragraph just like that?

610
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:57,110
This flattery is way too obvious.

611
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:01,850
Beautiful poem!

612
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,880
Using flowers to symbolize people,

613
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,080
subtle yet profound.

614
00:34:06,110 --> 00:34:06,840
Consort Xie,

615
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:11,920
you truly embody scholarly elegance.

616
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:15,960
No wonder the Emperor favors you so much.

617
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,850
Thank you for your praise, Your Majesty.

618
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:23,150
Unlike some people

619
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:26,110
who lack proper manners.

620
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:30,000
Why must everything involve me?

621
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:35,239
What Flower Festival Banquet?

622
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:38,280
I think they're just bored
and want to waste money.

623
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:40,480
Common people can barely afford to eat,

624
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:43,710
yet they still have time
for such frivolities.

625
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,800
This isn't the way back to the palace.

626
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:51,110
I didn't dare call out to you
since you were walking this way

627
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:52,239
with your head down.

628
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:52,920
No wonder.

629
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:54,270
-Let's—
-Consort Yu.

630
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,970
The palace is so large,

631
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:01,590
yet somehow I run into him everywhere.

632
00:35:01,590 --> 00:35:02,440
Such bad luck.

633
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:03,820
Your Highness.

634
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,580
Consort Yu.

635
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,550
May I have a word with you?
